To install wayland and associated tools I did the following

# Tools exchange
- Wayland
- Xserver + i3 -> Hyprland
- Polybar -> Waybar
- Feh -> Hyprpaper

# Commands
```bash
sudo pacman -S wayland
sudo pacman -S hyprland
sudo pacman -S waypaper
yay -S qt5-wayland qt5ct libva nvidia-vaapi-driver-git
sudo systemctl start seatd
sudo usermod -a -G seat <user>
yay -S waybar-hyprland-git
pacman -S xdg-desktop-portal-hyprland pipewire wireplumber qt6-wayland xdg-desktop-portal-wlr
```
